#. type: Title =
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Regions: Adjusting regions\n"
msgstr "領域: 領域の調整\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:5
msgid "[4 of 10](Regions-Feathering.html)"
msgstr "[4 of 10](Regions-Feathering.html)"

#. type: Plain text
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:9
msgid ""
"The shape of regions in LightZone can be adjusted at any time. When "
"initially creating regions, you can do a \"rough approximation\"; then, if "
"needed, you can go back and adjust them."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title -
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "To adjust the shape of a region:\n"
msgstr "領域の形を調整するには:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1.  '
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:22
msgid ""
"Click the Regions button in the [tool bar](Tools-Controls.html).  (The "
"region kind buttons will appear to the right of the tool bar and the regions "
"for the tool will become visible on your photo.)"
msgstr "[ツール バー](Tools-Controls.html)で領域ボタンをクリックします。(The region kind buttons will appear to the right of the tool bar and the regions for the tool will become visible on your photo.)"

#. type: Bullet: '2.  '
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:22
msgid ""
"![image](images/Region-Edit.png) Double-click the region whose shape you "
"want to adjust. (The control points will become visible.)"
msgstr "![image](images/Region-Edit.png) 形を調整したい領域をダブルクリックします。(調整点が見えるようになります。)"

#. type: Bullet: '3.  '
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:22
msgid "Drag a control point until it's in the desired location."
msgstr "調整点をドラッグして位置を合わせます。"

#. type: Bullet: '4.  '
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:22
msgid "Repeat from step 3 for every control point you want to adjust."
msgstr "調整したい調整点すべてで上記の 3 ステップを繰り返します。"

#. type: Bullet: '5.  '
#: Regions-Adjusting.markdown.txt:22
msgid ""
"When done, you can either click anywhere outside the region, or press either "
"the **return** or **esc** (escape) key."
msgstr "完了したら、領域の外をクリックするか、**Return** または **ESC** キーを押します。"
